    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A wormhole has opened up letting aliens terrorize your city. Pilot your spacecraft and destroy the aliens using flamethrowers, missiles, gatling guns, shockwaves, and more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232130/extras/b99b5da233b578a7488f6cfba0d13c97.poster.avif?t=1732331022\" width=616 height=132 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232130/extras/b99b5da233b578a7488f6cfba0d13c97.webm?t=1732331022\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232130/extras/b99b5da233b578a7488f6cfba0d13c97.mp4?t=1732331022\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232130/extras/1a14f5cde056dff103af6b861464e7d1.poster.avif?t=1732331022\" width=616 height=616 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232130/extras/1a14f5cde056dff103af6b861464e7d1.webm?t=1732331022\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232130/extras/1a14f5cde056dff103af6b861464e7d1.mp4?t=1732331022\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use a variety of weapons, abilities, and other power-ups to help you survive from <strong>flinging asteroids</strong> at your foes to <strong>lobbing black holes</strong>, <strong>incinerating</strong> your enemies<strong>,</strong> and using <strong>shockwaves</strong>. There are a dozen powerups to help you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232130/extras/bdb8276c8b35281a80bc40484b7c1eb7.poster.avif?t=1732331022\" width=616 height=132 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232130/extras/bdb8276c8b35281a80bc40484b7c1eb7.webm?t=1732331022\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232130/extras/bdb8276c8b35281a80bc40484b7c1eb7.mp4?t=1732331022\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232130/extras/12f970c4f8c44c1cf13b1a901cd129eb.poster.avif?t=1732331022\" width=616 height=616 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232130/extras/12f970c4f8c44c1cf13b1a901cd129eb.webm?t=1732331022\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232130/extras/12f970c4f8c44c1cf13b1a901cd129eb.mp4?t=1732331022\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A unique boss waiting for you at the end that mimics your movements, powerups, and weapons against you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232130/extras/b6a341a0b3910cd089feaaa49ef35043.poster.avif?t=1732331022\" width=616 height=132 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232130/extras/b6a341a0b3910cd089feaaa49ef35043.webm?t=1732331022\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232130/extras/b6a341a0b3910cd089feaaa49ef35043.mp4?t=1732331022\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232130/extras/6b684e426246b1e6bceeb744936107f7.avif?t=1732331022\" width=616 height=350 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use a variety of ships to change your gameplay. Each comes with a <strong>unique weapon </strong>and a basic powerup ability to complement. Teleport around with an<strong> Energy</strong> <strong>Gatling</strong>, go methodical slowing time for your exploding <strong>Lightning Orbs, </strong>go aggressive charging in with a <strong>Laser Torch</strong>, and more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232130/extras/67ba03de314ea06bffe1109b3a33d8f9.poster.avif?t=1732331022\" width=616 height=132 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232130/extras/67ba03de314ea06bffe1109b3a33d8f9.webm?t=1732331022\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232130/extras/67ba03de314ea06bffe1109b3a33d8f9.mp4?t=1732331022\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232130/extras/fab8e196c6dff9a49c1a8da73972a8d9.avif?t=1732331022\" width=616 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Avoid and destroy three different enemy types. Swarmers will overwhelm and charge you, Zappers will orbit around and shock you, and Devourers will strike and split while spewing acid.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Created for Godot Wild Jam #69</h2>",
